    <div class="container-fluid big-card-layout mb-5">
        <div class="individual-big-card container-sm">
            <div style="position: relative;" class="big-card-layout-image-1 chickpea-curry">
                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-5 col-xxl-4 card text-center perspective-card" id="card1">
                    <img class="card-img-top" src="/Images/Main Dishes/chichpea curry masala.jpg" alt="Chickpea Curry">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Chickpea Curry (Chana Masala)</h5>
                        <p>
                            <small>
                                Serving Size: 14 oz | Calories: 350 kcal
                            </small>
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Chickpeas are a great source of plant-based protein and require minimal water to grow compared to regular animal products, making them a significant alternative. Our chickpeas are sourced from our own farm, which practices organic, natural farming to ensure minimal chemical usage and the protection of our environment.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a style="color: var(--accent-color);">$10.00</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="individual-big-card container-sm">
            <div style="position: relative;" class="big-card-layout-image-2 aloo-gobi">
                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-5 col-xxl-4 offset-lg-6 offset-xl-7 offset-xxl-8 card text-center perspective-card" id="card1">
                    <img class="card-img-top" src="/Images/Main Dishes/potato and cauliflower curry (aloo gobi).jpg" alt="Potato & Cauliflower Curry">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Potato & Cauliflower Curry (Aloo Gobi)</h5>
                        <p>
                            <small>
                                Serving Size: 14 oz | Calories: 280 kcal
                            </small>
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Potatoes and cauliflower are rugged, low-impact crops that excel in the regional Texas environment. We source these vegetables from local farms supporting locally owned businesses. We can also certify that these vegetables were grown with water conservation in mind, utilizing drip irrigation.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a style="color: var(--accent-color);">$9.50</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="individual-big-card container-sm">
            <div style="position: relative;" class="big-card-layout-image-3 eggplant-mash">
                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-5 col-xxl-4 card text-center perspective-card" id="card1">
                    <img class="card-img-top" src="/Images/Main Dishes/eggplantn mash.jpg" alt="Smoked Eggplant Mash">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Smoked Eggplant Mash (Baingan Bharta)</h5>
                        <p>
                            <small>
                                Serving Size: 12 oz | Calories: 250 kcal
                            </small>
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Our eggplants were grown with sustainable methods, such as composting and crop rotation. These techniques are important to improve soil health and reduce the need for artificial fertilizers. The smokiness comes from grilling over an open flame to provide you with a culturally authentic taste.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a style="color: var(--accent-color);">$9.50</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="individual-big-card container-sm">
            <div style="position: relative;" class="big-card-layout-image-4 tikka-masala">
                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-5 col-xxl-4 offset-lg-6 offset-xl-7 offset-xxl-8 card text-center perspective-card" id="card1">
                    <img class="card-img-top" src="/Images/Main Dishes/vegan tikka masala.jpg" alt="Tikka Masala">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Vegan Tikka Masala</h5>
                        <p>
                            <small>
                                Serving Size: 14 oz | Calories: 400 kcal
                            </small>
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Using locally sourced tofu instead of the animal based paneer we were able to create the same flavorful dish but with respect to our environment. We have also decided on using organic local spices to minimize transportation pollution.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a style="color: var(--accent-color);">$11.00</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="individual-big-card container-sm">
            <div style="position: relative;" class="big-card-layout-image-4 spiced-flatbread">
