                    <img class="card-img-top" src="/Images/Main Dishes/spiced flatbread.jpg" alt="Spiced Flatbread">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Spiced Flatbread (Methi Thepla)</h5>
                        <p>
                            <small>
                                Serving Size: 12 oz | Calories: 350 kcal
                            </small>
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            This flatbread is made from whole wheat flour and fenugreek leaves, both of which are sourced from our very own yard  practicing organic and sustainable agriculture. Fenugreek, known for its soil-enriching properties, helps support sustainable farming practices
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a style="color: var(--accent-color);">$9.50 (4 Pieces)</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
