                    <img class="card-img-top" src="/Images/Main Dishes/sweet and sour curry.jpg" alt="Sweet & Sour Curry">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Vegan Sweet & Sour Curry (Vegan Vindaloo)</h5>
                        <p>
                            <small>
                                Serving Size: 14 oz | Calories: 400 kcal
                            </small>
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Tofu or tempeh is sourced from local producers who use non-GMO, soybeans grown with sustainable farming practices. Our sweet & sour curry is made with organic vinegar and locally grown vegetables, minimizing the need for long-distance transportation.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a style="color: var(--accent-color);">$10.50</a>
                    </div>
