                    <img class="card-img-top" src="/Images/Main Dishes/lentil stew.jpg" alt="Lentil Stew">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Lentil Stew (Daal Tadka)</h5>
                        <p>
                            <small>
                                Serving Size: 14 oz | Calories: 300 kcal
                            </small>
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Lentils are an excellent sustainable crop that enriches the soil by fixing nitrogen. Our lentils are sourced from nearby organic farms practicing crop rotation and low-impact farming methods. The dish is cooked using minimal oil and served with locally sourced rice.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a style="color: var(--accent-color);">$9.50</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="individual-big-card container-sm">
            <div style="position: relative;" class="big-card-layout-image-4 potato-and-pea-curry">
                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-5 col-xxl-4 card text-center perspective-card" id="card1">
                    <img class="card-img-top" src="/Images/Main Dishes/potato and pea curry.jpg" alt="Potato & Pea Curry">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Potato & Pea Curry (Aloo Matar)</h5>
                        <p>
                            <small>
                                Serving Size: 14 oz | Calories: 300 kcal
                            </small>
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Potatoes and peas are both resilient crops with low environmental impact. We source them from local farms that prioritize regenerative agricultural practices, reducing their carbon footprint and reliance on synthetic chemicals.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a style="color: var(--accent-color);">$9.50</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="individual-big-card container-sm">
            <div style="position: relative;" class="big-card-layout-image-4 veg-biryani">
                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-5 col-xxl-4 offset-lg-6 offset-xl-7 offset-xxl-8 card text-center perspective-card" id="card1">
                    <img class="card-img-top" src="/Images/Main Dishes/vegetable biryani.jpg" alt="Vegetable Biryani">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Vegan Vegetable Biryani (Vegan Pulao Biryani)</h5>
                        <p>
                            <small>
                                Serving Size: 18 oz | Calories: 500 kcal
                            </small>
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Our biryani is made using organic basmati rice and a variety of seasonal vegetables from local farmers. The dish is prepared using minimal energy-efficient cooking methods, reducing our overall energy consumption.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        <a style="color: var(--accent-color);">$12.00</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
